{"tid":2308683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★澳門博彩】傳博監局與業界初步討論 數字化人民幣或可換籌碼","createTime":"2020-12-02T05:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T07:22:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9d314e4026fbd794cbe2a6816b562e5ee321b3","tid":2308683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2817830/31231_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2817830%2F31231_600.png&h=824aee78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，澳門有部分賭場經營者，已經獲澳門博監局人員接觸，商討數字化人民幣兌換籌碼，目前討論只是在初步階段。<br />\n<br />\n近期澳門博彩業受新冠肺炎影響，加上內地收緊資金賭博的途徑，令澳門博彩業特別是中介人面對巨大壓力。早前瑞信發表報告，指市場對澳門博彩業復甦或過度樂觀。假如數字化人民幣獲得採納，有助開拓澳門以外的市場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，澳門博監局針對博彩業開拓市場的問題，於上月中指雖然網上博彩可以提高博彩收益，但會帶來洗黑錢及賭博成癮的問題，澳門在引入網上賭博時，需要審慎考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2817830/【澳門博彩】傳博監局與業界初步討論%20%20%20%20數字化人民幣或可換籌碼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2817830%2F%E3%80%90%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%8D%9A%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%8D%9A%E7%9B%A3%E5%B1%80%E8%88%87%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%2520%2520%2520%2520%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E5%8C%96%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E6%8F%9B%E7%B1%8C%E7%A2%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2eu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=43d8ae38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2817830/【澳門博彩】傳博監局與業界初步討論%20%20%20%20數字化人民幣或可換籌碼？</a>"},{"pid":"6b32861f23350b54d4ef968d9c7600d265f55894","tid":2308683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class